Fork of HandmadeIMAP
~~~~~~~~~~~~

This fork is based on HandmadeIMAP by Pete Warden. It was intented to simplify gmail
connection process using oAuth for authentication. Main focus of this branch is to 
provide a clean and simple library for connecting to gmail and performing basic
operations on its IMAP.
Feel free to contact me via github or <paulina.budzon@gmail.com>

